OL,3,CMinister facing prospect of jail over
OL,4,C#10k church fraud
OL,6,FA minister is facing a potential jail
OL,7,Fsentence after he was convicted him of
OL,8,Fdefrauding #10,000 from his church.
OL,10,FStanding in the dock of Craigavon
OL,11,FCrown Court, Rev. Adrian McLaughlin
OL,12,Flooked stunned as the jury foreperson
OL,13,Fannounced the 10-2 majority verdict
OL,14,Fthat the 50-year-old was guilty of
OL,15,Ffraud by abuse of position.
OL,17,FThe jury of 10 men and two women had
OL,18,Fdeliberated for just over six hours
OL,19,Fover the course of two days before
OL,20,Fdeclaring the Church of Ireland
OL,21,Fminister guilty.
