OL,6,FRev. McLaughlin was charged with
OL,7,Fabusing his position of trust at St
OL,8,FColman's Parish Church in Dunmurry.
OL,10,FHe was found to have written a cheque
OL,11,Ffor #10,000 from the church bank
OL,12,Faccount which he then made payable to
OL,13,Fhimself.
OL,15,FThe jury heard that while Rev.
OL,16,FMcLaughlin claimed the money was to
OL,17,Freimburse him for money he spent
OL,18,Fhimself on the "beautification and
OL,19,Fbetterment" of St Colman's parish.
