OL,6,FFollowing the jury's verdict Judge
OL,7,FPatrick Lynch KC thanked them for
OL,8,Ftheir "deep consideration" of the case
OL,9,Fand advised them that he would be
OL,10,Fpassing sentence "at some further
OL,11,Fstage" once pre-sentence reports had
OL,12,Fbeen prepared.
OL,14,FWhile Rev. McLaughlin, from Church
OL,15,FAvenue in Dunmurry, was freed on bail
OL,16,Funtil 6 September, Judge Lynch warned
OL,17,Fhim his release "is no indication of
OL,18,Fwhat the ultimate sentence of the
OL,19,Fcourt will be".
